{"tid":2393690,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"何栢良重申：政府防疫要科學","createTime":"2021-02-03T15:31:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T21:23:56.000Z","uid":5195,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b5cc96a8dba123bc39e5a38011583a84e8011f6c","tid":2393690,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T15:31:14.000Z","msg":"港大感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良在同一節目指，第三原因是效率低，周二被封的天水圍天恒邨恒樂樓早在上月24日已有確診，至今8人染疫，但至昨日才封鎖，認為政府在出現首宗個案時，就應在大廈門外設檢測街站，<br />\n<br />\n何續稱，佐敦、深水埗及油麻地有不少公廁，有不屬於當區的患者使用後離開，影響了檢測準確率，質疑封區不符合成本效益，而深水埗及油麻地近日確診回落，相信是與強制檢測有關，與封區關係不大。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">他重申，防疫要科學，封區應針對高危地方，但現時數據不足以支持圍封，如果政府採取沒有科學數據支持的措施，將有壞的影響。</span>"},{"pid":"4354a0265b1bca4d0d6f480d6b60e5fc6b37a0e3","tid":2393690,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T15:35:46.000Z","msg":"我就係科學<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3uRFtkH.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3uRFtkH.gif&h=79516f94&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Uh9PmFz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUh9PmFz.jpg&h=e7d9b1bf&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0XASjse.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0XASjse.jpg&h=709b91bc&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sG5V1FA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsG5V1FA.png&h=addcba20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你地班蟻民係咪極端反科學分子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\